name: Västervik
overview: Västervik, located in Sweden, is celebrated for its granite rock that offers a variety of bouldering opportunities. This coastal area is well-known for its picturesque setting, where climbers can enjoy both seaside and forested routes. Västervik's popularity lies in its granite formations, making it an appealing destination year-round.

Västervik, situado en Suecia, es celebrado por su roca de granito que ofrece una variedad de oportunidades de boulder. Esta área costera es conocida por su entorno pintoresco, donde los escaladores pueden disfrutar de rutas junto al mar y en el bosque.
